Hi! I use latest source MonoGame from develop branch for my engine and visual editor. After the latest update I get the error NullReferenceException in MonoGame.Framework in PlatformSetup() function, at line 122.
var wnd = (Game.Instance.Window as OpenTKGameWindow).Window.WindowInfo;

Game.Instance is null. I do not create Game object for Winforms control. Please tell me how to solve this problem.
